# PMM Kit ships as a framework only: this file, CLAUDE.md, README.md, and .claude/skills/.
# Everything else — personalized context, raw inputs, and per-product hubs — is private
# by default. This uses an allow-list: ignore everything, then explicitly un-ignore the
# framework paths. New product hub folders (named after the product) are ignored
# automatically without needing to be added here.

/*
!/.claude/
!/.claude/**
!/CLAUDE.md
!/README.md
!/.gitignore
!/context/
!/context/README.md

# Local session/permission config — machine-specific, never shared
/.claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/settings.local.json

# OS cruft
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
